nodeDescription.value: Gets a unique identity verification URL from AuthenticID and starts a flow challenge that resolves when the user completes verification in the secondary flow
Waits for a webhook call from AuthenticID with the status of the verification request
Converts the unique verification URL to a QR code image
Displays the QR code image and waits for the challenge status to change when the secondary flow completes
Triggers the main flow to continue
Shows the result of the verification process
This node could call other flows to move forward to any process.

annotation.value: Provide a verification URL to the user
When verification is complete, show an error or trigger the main flow to continue
Branch the flow based on the verification result
Wait for the user to complete verification
